  "recommendations": [
    "Jiexi \"Jesse\" Huang\n\nI had the pleasure of working with Judd from from 2009 through 2013 while he was a Project Manager at Daktronics, Inc. Judd exemplifies what a great project manager should be working in an international environment. He is dedicated, pragmatic, and has an eye for detail. However, it's Judd's presence as a leader which is his best quality. Whether it's leading by example or taking charge in a crisis, Judd is always someone that management and other staff can count on to make the right decisions at the right time. He communicates well across multiple cultures and has contributed invaluably to Daktronics' success in the Asia Pacific Region. I recommend him without reservation."
  ],
